                <head>South Carolina Convention</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"The proceedings of the South Carolina 'Sovereign Convention' on Monday,
                    the 24th, so far as made public, were not interesting or important."</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Article disapproves of South Carolina's secession convention.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
